  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Employing EU citizens in the UK
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Information for employers on employing EU, EEA and Swiss citizens in the UK, covering: right to work checks, the EU Settlement Scheme and the UK’s new immigration system. </p>

  </div>
</div>

